window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Genesis Online has added a new feature that allows players to purchase land and build homes or businesses.</b></p> <p>Using the gold he collected while fighting Itrix, Kevin buys a plot of land with visions of creating a settlement that will help him make money playing the game. He plans to buy a neural interface, hoping it will help with his recovery from the accident that left him unable to walk.</p> <p>Unfortunately, other players, both within his guild and outside of it, have other plans. He has to work hard to prevent a new enemy from stealing the supplies he needs to build up the town. At the same time, members of his own guild question his decisions and threaten to destroy everything he is working towards. Can he find a way to solve his problems and accomplish his goals?</p>"; 
